  "title": "说脏话牛奶",
  "summary": "by 新世界的大门",
  "content": "<p>今天，我饮用<a href=\"https://en.wiktionary.org/wiki/%E8%AA%AA%E9%AB%92%E8%A9%B1#Chinese\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">说脏话牛奶</a><sup><a href=\"https://blog.xinshijiededa.men/daily/6/#user-content-fn-1\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">1</a></sup>，然后如厕。</p>\n<h2>---<a href=\"https://blog.xinshijiededa.men/daily/6/#footnote-label\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><span>#</span></a></h2>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>《星岛头条》，<a href=\"https://www.stheadline.com/food/3436289/%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E6%82%85%E9%AE%AE%E6%B4%BB%E9%AE%AE%E5%A5%B6%E9%80%B2%E9%A7%90%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%A4%96%E8%99%9F%E8%AA%AA%E9%AB%92%E8%A9%B11%E5%8E%9F%E5%9B%A0%E6%AF%94%E6%9C%AC%E5%90%8D%E7%88%86%E7%B4%85-%E4%B9%B3%E7%B3%96%E4%B8%8D%E8%80%90%E7%97%87%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91%E5%AF%A7%E9%A1%98%E6%8B%89%E8%82%9A%E5%AD%90%E4%B9%9F%E6%83%B3%E5%96%9D\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">內地「悅鮮活」鮮奶進駐香港！外號「&#x27;&#x27;&#x27;說髒話&#x27;&#x27;&#x27;」1原因比本名爆紅 乳糖不耐症網民：寧願拉肚子也想喝！</a>，2025-03-10 <a href=\"https://blog.xinshijiededa.men/daily/6/#user-content-fnref-1\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">↩</a></p>\n</li>\n</ol>",
